      "side": 1,
      "message": "It\u0027s because this is trying to follow the client example code snippet from go/result-sink-protocol as much as possible.\n\nMy original intention was\n(1) sink_test.go contains unit tests with real HTTP interactions, which clients would have sent out.\n(2) sink_server_test.go, which is the unit test module of the prpc server methods, contains unit tests with mocked prpc server and clients.\n\nIf go/result-sink-protocol adds another example snippet using prpc#Client, then I can change this to use prpc#Client, instead. WDTY?",
